Sublime Text:
ctrl+m			#skip around inside paranthesis
ctrl+q			#expand selection to quotes
ctrl+l			#highlight current line
ctrl+j			#bring next line up by removing newline character at the end of current line
ctrl+shift+up/down	#to move lines up/down

ctrl+shift+space	#highlight everything in bracket
ctrl+enter		#insert and focus to new line below current line.
ctrl+X			#cut line
ctrl+K/ctrl+shift+K	#delete to EoL/start of line
edit /home/ocean/.config/sublime-text-3/Packages/User/Package Control.sublime-settings	#to install package, because it seems package control doesn't work.
